<div class="txtlevel"><p>Proiect de testare pentru studentii din grupa 232.</p></div>
 <br/><a name='toc_1'></a>
<h1 class='doclevel'>1.Test Suite : dsir3517_WBT</h1>
<div><p>Se testeaza functionalitatea de filtrare dupa pret a produselor din cadrul aplicatiei.</p>
</div><a name="toc_tc30224"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P232-63: filterByPretTestCase1&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">dsir3517</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Verificarea functionalitatii de filtrare dupa pret atunci cand exista cel putin un produs in intervalul specificat. Se testeaza daca sistemul returneaza corect produsele din interval.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><ul>
	<li>Sistemul este pornit si lista de produse este initializata.</li>
	<li>Lista contine produse: p1(id=1, nume=&quot;c&quot;, pret=10.0, categorie=TEA, tip=BASIC), p2(id=2, nume=&quot;a&quot;, pret=20.0, categorie=JUICE, tip=BASIC).</li>
	<li>Date de intrare: pretMinim = 5, pretMaxim = 15.</li>
</ul>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Automated</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" >MyDrinkShop.ServiceClass</td></tr>
<tr><td > name of the test method:</td><td  colspan = "3" >MyDrinkShop.ServiceClass.filterByPret#1</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Requirements</span><td colspan="3">dsir3517_F02:  FiltrarePret [Version : 1]<br /></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Keywords:</span></td><td colspan="3">&nbsp;None<br/></td></tr>
</table>
</div>
<a name="toc_tc30226"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P232-64: filterByPretTestCase2&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">dsir3517</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Verificarea functionalitatii de filtrare dupa pret in situatia in care pretul minim este mai mare decat pretul maxim. Se testeaza daca sistemul arunca exceptia corespunzatoare.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><ul>
	<li>Sistemul este pornit si lista de produse este initializata.</li>
	<li>Lista contine produse: p1(id=1, nume=&quot;c&quot;, pret=10.0, categorie=TEA, tip=BASIC).</li>
	<li>Date de intrare: pretMinim = 20, pretMaxim = 10.</li>
</ul>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Automated</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" >MyDrinkShop.ServiceClass</td></tr>
<tr><td > name of the test method:</td><td  colspan = "3" >MyDrinkShop.ServiceClass.filterByPret#2</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Requirements</span><td colspan="3">dsir3517_F02:  FiltrarePret [Version : 1]<br /></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Keywords:</span></td><td colspan="3">&nbsp;None<br/></td></tr>
